				p(style="font-size:16px") The FES Watch, which is praised highly by Mr. Kazuo Hirai and will hit China market this year, was born in Sony's Seed Acceleration Program (SAP). However, do you know that the FES Watch project leader, Mr. Sugiyama, was originally a television engineer of Sony? On the 20th anniversary of Sony China(SCN), to explore those potential new business and take roots in China, SCN has established special project committee to introduce such a kind of "bottom-up" innovation proposal mechanism into China--- 2016 “Inspire Innovation-Sony China（IISC）” business innovation event has officially kicked off in SCN. 
				br
				p(style="font-size:16px") Based on a series of introduction activities, IISC will firstly collect new business idea and proposals both concerning on new business and research from all sectors of SCN. The committee will then select some outstanding cases and take exhibitions in Shanghai and Beijing office. Eventually, the cases will be evaluated by the top managers, while awards and prizes, including Top Management Prize, Outstanding Prize, will be issued. More importantly, after the awarding ceremony, SCN top managers encourage good idea presenters to communicate with certain departments to apply event results to business practices and gain practical benefits.
				br
				p(style="font-size:16px") SCN top managers have given a strong support on this large-scale annual innovation event. With regard to the activity, Mr.Takahashi encouraged that: “The overlapping part between corporate resources and customer needs is where our business chances lie on. Though in the fast-growing Chinese market, there are still many opportunities that we have not yet fully excavated.” IoT, VR，internet plus…… how to combine these IN words, also the technological hot topics with Chinese market and ignite the brand-new spark? Perhaps you have such business opportunities around you, but you have been failing to point them out. Or you have got a new business idea but nowhere to express it. Inspiring thinking and innovation, providing show stage, IISC is expecting your participation and excellent performance!				
